<td>Based on product characteristics</td>
<td>Some categories are gender-neutral</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Location</td>
<td>Core cities in target markets</td>
<td>Can exclude high-return-rate regions</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Device</td>
<td>Mobile-first (&gt;95% share)</td>
<td>iOS users typically have higher LTV</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
