<h2>VI. Data Analysis and ROI Optimization</h2>
<h3>6.1 Core KPI Monitoring Framework</h3>
<p><strong>Brand Awareness KPIs</strong>:<br />
- Impressions<br />
- Reach<br />
- Video Completion Rate</p>
<p><strong>Engagement KPIs</strong>:<br />
- Click-Through Rate (CTR): TikTok industry average 1-2%<br />
- Like/Comment/Share rates</p>
<p><strong>Conversion KPIs</strong>:<br />
- Cost Per Click (CPC): $0.2-0.8<br />
- Cost Per Acquisition (CPA): $5-50+ (highly category-dependent)<br />
- Return on Ad Spend (ROAS)</p>
<h3>6.2 ROAS Calculation and Optimization Logic</h3>
<p><strong>Basic Formula</strong>:</p>
<pre><code>ROAS = Total Revenue from Ads / Ad Spend
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Decomposed Optimization</strong>:</p>
<pre><code>ROAS = (CTR × CVR × AOV × Repeat Purchase Rate) / (CPC × Conversion Rate Discount)
</code></pre>
<p>Five levers to improve ROAS:</p>
<ol>
<li><strong>Increase CTR</strong>: Optimize creative quality and audience matching</li>
<li><strong>Boost CVR</strong>: Improve landing page experience and load speed</li>
<li><strong>Raise AOV</strong>: Through promotional bundles and upsells</li>
<li><strong>Increase Repeat Purchase Rate</strong>: Email remarketing, Retargeting</li>
<li><strong>Reduce CPC</strong>: Optimize bidding strategies and creative quality scores</li>
</ol>
<h3>6.3 The Power of Retargeting</h3>
<p>Research shows <strong>retargeting users convert at 5-10x the rate of new users</strong>. Implement layered retargeting:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Layer 1 (Within 3 days)</strong>: Serve limited-time discounts to AddToCart non-purchasers</li>
<li><strong>Layer 2 (Within 7 days)</strong>: Deliver educational content about products to website visitors</li>
<li><strong>Layer 3 (Within 30 days)</strong>: Push new products or accessories to past purchasers</li>
</ul>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>Case Data</strong>: A home goods brand implemented a three-stage retargeting funnel, achieving ROAS of <strong>1:8.5</strong> on retargeting ads, significantly higher than the 1:2.3 from new customer acquisition.</p>
</blockquote>
